-- Migration: {{.title}}
-- Work Item: {{.work_item_id}}
-- Created: $(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)

-- FAIL-CLOSED TEMPLATE: replace the guarded block below with concrete migration SQL before applying.
